I don&#39;t think its that Michelle. I think it is because a lot of us do this for different reason than you. I for one do not do this to prove a point or make this real to the world. Everyone will find that out sooner or later. I do this and other psi experimentation to expand my consciousness and to improve myself. The contacts and relationships I have built through ITC both on this side and the next are what I am interested in. So much of this research will never be proven because it takes so much personal involvement to make it work. It is not the equipment but the person who is making the connection and not one open minded skeptic, skeptic or close minded skeptic will accept personal accounts as proof.

That is what I take from Sumption&#39;s comments. It is pointless or spinning your wheels to fool yourself into believing people will accept what many of us already know.

Regards,

Frank R.

