            Really??? Pointless? Is that the majority thought here, that it

doesn&#39;t matter? That there&#39;s no room for improvement? No need for

standards or protocols? 

The utter anger and refusal to post raw files concerns me and probably

a few others but, maybe not. My suggestions and questions are valid

and should at least be considered regardless of what you think about me. 

The whole &quot;Babs has Issues&quot; was a tongue in cheek title for the

thread, knowing what some of you think of me. I thought it was funny

but apparently not. It is clear that some of you will not get past

that and consider my observations. My sincere thanks to those of you

who are able to.



Babs



