&gt; &gt; &gt;     &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt;             Alright, you all know I&#39;m vocal and I haven&#39;t made any&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &quot;friends&quot; here&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
