&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; Spirit communication has been my passion since day one, a little &lt;br&gt;
&gt; over&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; 6 years ago. I am a believer in the afterlife and a believer in&lt;br&gt;
