&gt; order&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; for me to believe something is paranormal I HAVE to rule out all &lt;br&gt;
&gt; other&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; possible causes. That being said, I have some questions. My hope &lt;br&gt;
&gt; is&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
