&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; I have a difficult time with many of the files here. Many times, &lt;br&gt;
&gt; there&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
