&gt; same&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; decibel as the question askers voice. Those two things should not&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; occur naturally considering the devices being used. That tells me &lt;br&gt;
