&gt; &gt; &gt; 650, 660 and maybe even 670. That extends the time a great deal. &lt;br&gt;
&gt; This&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; is a difficult problem because it is almost impossible for the &lt;br&gt;
&gt; average&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;br&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; person to be able to make a determination on time this way. &lt;br&gt;
